videos.description: Tyler Huntley launches a pass downfield to a wide-open Demari Simpkins who gets all the way down to the 9-yard line. The Utes would score a touchdown later in the drive.
videos.headline: Utah airs it out for 71 yards into Washington State red zone

videos.description: Luke Falk becomes the all-time leader in the PAC-12 for touchdowns thrown with this short touchdown throw to Kyle Sweet.
videos.headline: Falk throws 2nd TD of first half

videos.description: Tyler Huntley tries to escape the rush and ends up throwing it into the waiting arms of Washington State's Hunter Dale to set up great field position.
videos.headline: Interception sets Cougars up in red zone

videos.description: Luke Falk connects with Isaiah Johnson-Mack for the 6-yard touchdown pass in the back of the end zone.
videos.headline: Falk throws 3rd TD of game

videos.description: Tyler Huntley throws to Raelon Singleton who is able to keep his feet in on the side of the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Nice foot drag for Utah TD
